description: The fund invests primarily in common stocks, depositary receipts and real estate investment trusts (REITs). The fund is not managed to an index and may invest in equity securities in both U.S. and foreign markets, including emerging markets. The fund may invest a significant portion of its assets in small capitalization companies and have significant positions in specific sectors or markets from time to time. It is non-diversified.
name: JPMorgan Social Advancement ETF
